        <p class="lead">
            This website was designed and created by the members of the Think Train organization as part of a 99 Hour project with the Karolinska Instiutet Centre for Gender Medicine in August 2014. The intention was to empower the public to better understanding of their gender specific reactions to commonly prescribed drugs based on FDA data. &nbsp;</p>
